V8

Not really interactive, but why rewrite good code?

library(V8)

ct <- new_context( "window" )
ct$eval ( 
  " console.log( ['I am in JavaScript. 1+1 = ', 1 + 1].join('') ) "
)
## I am in JavaScript. 1+1 = 2

htmlwidgets - Leaflet

m %>% setView( -86.8034743, 33.5025432, zoom=17 )
